{"tid":165116,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[自癒系] 刀仔切沙有乜好睇？ 拍片者就咁紅佐","createTime":"2017-03-21T06:31:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T02:49:52.000Z","uid":21267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"200ea746863b5beba25626069d7d885dd924a732","tid":165116,"uid":21267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T06:31:32.000Z","msg":"網上一段普通不過的斬沙片，只是不斷重複用刀切沙，卻讓人不知不覺間看完，不少人更覺得非常療癒！<br />\n<br />\n從「sand.isfying」上載的片段可見，片中人用刀將五顏六色、不同形狀的沙磚，一刀一刀切成方塊沙片，切口非常整齊，被切出的沙塊亦凝而不散，猶如魔術一樣。他亦會用刀捅入、徒手捏散或用剪刀剪散沙磚等，總之要將形狀完好的沙磚完全摧毀。<br />\n這種特別的沙叫作「動力沙」，是一種兒童沙粒玩具，由98%沙和2%聚二甲基矽氧烷（PDMS）組成，像黏土一樣可以被塑造成不同形狀，但只會黏其他動力沙，不會黏手或乾掉。<br />\n有網民看過後指片段有助放鬆心情，其Instagram帳戶有逾30萬人關注。有專家解釋這現象源於「自發性知覺高潮反應」（ASMR），即聽到或看到特定的東西後人們會產生愉悅反應。不過，亦有人狠批浪費了人生的3分鐘。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IcErh6xW7MQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIcErh6xW7MQ&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnufjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=5be672db\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IcErh6xW7MQ</a>"},{"pid":"6f64ca8cec97b4d61412cd158d0ea64e7b812431","tid":165116,"uid":21267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b30c77e7f1f53f7ad6e6933bf35781e77ebe6fa0","tid":165116,"uid":21267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T04:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2167245383fd366fc291a2d5a1a9be99a5c2bf1a","tid":165116,"uid":21267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T16:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b50d70a5e4bd87477f0a70534bc00ae8b02233","tid":165116,"uid":21267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}